dataset.title: Studies of the genus Anthelephila (Coleoptera: Anthicidae) 13. The species described by W. W. Saunders from India

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Kejval, Zbyněk (2015): Studies of the genus Anthelephila (Coleoptera: Anthicidae) 13. The species described by W. W. Saunders from India. Acta Entomologica Musei Nationalis Pragae 55 (1): 249-260, DOI: http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5319048
